data.description: Just stunning, and beautifully designed floor plan!!!  A beautiful craftsman style one story home available now in the highly desirable west side of Hemet. Conveniently located within quick access to Domenigoni Pkwy and I-215. This home was built in 2006. Its features include four bedrooms, two bathrooms, almost 2500 sqft of living space, three car garage, nicely maintained front and back yard. As you enter into this home a spacious formal living room and dining room will welcome you. As you continue,  you will  find a cozy family room and a strategically located fire place facing the kitchen. In the kitchen, granite counter tops, stainless steel utility sink, lots of cabinets for extra storage, and a designated desk area, perfect while working from home. Lost of natural lighting.   The  spacious master bedroom suite  has a walk-in closet, his and hers sink, private restroom, and a separate shower and tub.  All rooms are very spacious. Tile in all bathrooms, living room, family room, kitchen and hallways. Carpet in all rooms. Utility sink and cabinets in laundry room located as you enter the home from garage door.  Buyer to assume 14 panel solar lease...Too much to mention it all... When you see it you will love it..Make it yours!! Motivated sellers...
